pair.value: The high level Control Process which controls the aspects of a CaRE from Scheduling through to outcome.

annotation.text:
This control process is initiated from the global action of scheduling a CaRE.
It initiates the maintain evaluation process with no variables, triggering it to capture data for a new evaluation. Once initiated, it launches sub processes to perform the care pre-evaluation, the risk assessment and the evaluation.
Listen for a message from the 'Cancel CaRE Evaluation' process and terminate this process if one is received.
